Package: misha.browser
Title: Interactive Genome Browser for Misha Tracks
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Aviezer", "Lifshitz", email = "aviezer.lifshitz@weizmann.ac.il", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Weizmann Institute of Science", role="cph")
    )
Author: Aviezer Lifshitz [aut, cre],
    Weizmann Institute of Science [cph]
Maintainer: Aviezer Lifshitz <aviezer.lifshitz@weizmann.ac.il>
Description: A configurable, interactive genome browser built on ggplot2 and
    patchwork. Provides YAML-based configuration for visualization of misha
    genomic tracks with support for custom transformations, faceting, vertical
    line annotations, and gene models. Includes a Shiny application for
    interactive exploration.
